'''Ning'''是一个用于创建自定义[[社交网站|社交网站]]的在线平台。<ref name="economist">[http://www.economist.com/business/displaystory.cfm?story_id=9990635 Social Graph-iti] {{Wayback|url=http://www.economist.com/business/displaystory.cfm?story_id=9990635 |date=20100205115924 }}, The Economist, Oct 18, 2007</ref><ref name="servicefeatures">[http://venturebeat.com/2011/02/02/ning-design-studio/ Ning adds lots of knobs and dials to prettify its custom social networks] {{Wayback|url=http://venturebeat.com/2011/02/02/ning-design-studio/ |date=20160523190932 }}, Anthony Ha, VentureBeat, Feb 2, 2011</ref><ref name="customerbase">[http://blog.ning.com/2011/06/the-ning-pov.html/ The Ning POV: How Custom Social Communities Can Change the World] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.ning.com/2011/06/the-ning-pov.html/ |date=20110623065619 }}, Christina Lee on June 21, 2011</ref>网站设置了照片、视频、[[论坛|论坛]]、博客等功能，并设有[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[Twitter|Twitter]]、[[Google|Google]]及[[雅虎|Yahoo!]]等网站的分享按钮。<ref name="servicefeatures"/><ref name="socialsigninjanrain">[http://techcrunch.com/2010/11/10/ning-partners-with-janrain-to-offer-social-sign-ins-to-users/ Ning Partners With Janrain To Offer Social Sign-Ins To Users] {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2010/11/10/ning-partners-with-janrain-to-offer-social-sign-ins-to-users/ |date=20160303224857 }}, Leena Rao, TechCrunch, Nov 10, 2010</ref> <span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="139"></span>

Ning由[[网景|网景]]创办人[[马克·安德森|马克·安德森]]和[[吉娜·比安奇尼|吉娜·比安奇尼]]于2005年10月共同创建。<ref name="Ning Blog"/>。截至2011年6月，已有超过90,000个社交网站依赖于Ning的平台运行。<ref name="networkcount3">[http://blogs.forbes.com/tomiogeron/2011/06/15/with-revenue-up-400-ning-adds-paid-access-service/ With Revenue Up 400%, Ning Adds Paid Access Service] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.forbes.com/tomiogeron/2011/06/15/with-revenue-up-400-ning-adds-paid-access-service/ |date=20110719025334 }}, Tomio Geron, Forbes, June 15, 2011</ref><ref name="networkcount2">[http://www.scribbal.com/2011/06/ning-announces-ustream-integration-into-social-websites/ Ning Announces Ustream Integration Into Social Websites] {{Wayback|url=http://www.scribbal.com/2011/06/ning-announces-ustream-integration-into-social-websites/ |date=20110626063713 }}, Mariel Loveland, Scribbal, June 7, 2011</ref>

Ning支持六种不同语言的转换，分别为：英语，意大利语，法语，德语，西班牙语和葡萄牙语。 <ref>{{cite web |author1=Ning |title=Ning Web |url=https://www.ning.com |website=Ning |accessdate=2018-12-19 |archive-date=2018-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218203136/https://www.ning.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 发展历史 ==
Ning最初是由Bianchini、Andreessen和[[天使投资者|天使投资者]]融资形成。

* 2004年10月开始开发其产品。
* 2005年10月对外发布服务。<ref name="cnet2005">[http://www.news.com/Andreessen-adds-some-Ning-to-the-Web/2100-1032_3-5890005.html?tag=st.nl Andreessen adds some Ning to the Web] {{Wayback|url=http://www.news.com/Andreessen-adds-some-Ning-to-the-Web/2100-1032_3-5890005.html?tag=st.nl |date=20191018223436 }}, by Martin LaMonica, CNET news, Oct 6, 2005</ref>
* 2006年9月下旬，Ning將照片與視頻列為重點發展項目。

* 2007年7月，Ning募集了四千四百万美元用于[[风险投资|风险投资]]。<ref name="pmarca">[http://blog.pmarca.com/2007/07/ning-news-new-i.html Ning news: new investment round] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.pmarca.com/2007/07/ning-news-new-i.html |date=20071020094534 }}, by Marc Andreesen, blog.pmarca.com, Jul 9, 2007</ref>

* 2008年和2009年，公司又募集了七千五百万美元用于风险投资。<ref name="Marc Andreessen">[http://blog.pmarca.com/2008/04/ning-news-serie.html Ning news: Series D investment round] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.pmarca.com/2008/04/ning-news-serie.html |date=20090129155521 }}, by Marc Andreessen, April 18, 2008</ref><ref name="Lightspeedinvestor">[http://allthingsd.com/20090721/ning-raises-15-million-more-at-a-yes-really-750-million-valuation/ Ning Raises $15 Million More at a–Yes, Really–$750 Million Valuation] {{Wayback|url=http://allthingsd.com/20090721/ning-raises-15-million-more-at-a-yes-really-750-million-valuation/ |date=20110801024628 }}, by Kara Swisher, AllThingsD.com, July 21, 2009</ref>

* 2010年4月15日，Ning的[[CEO|CEO]]宣布停止免费服务，并解雇了69名员工。

现在Ning已拥有九万客户。<ref name="networkcount3"/>其客户包括[[聯合公園|聯合公園]]、<ref name="linkinpark">[http://blog.ning.com/2011/03/south-by-southwest-back.html/ South by Southwest & Back] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.ning.com/2011/03/south-by-southwest-back.html/ |date=20110827092650 }}, Erika Gessin on March 24, 2011</ref>[[威瑟樂團|威瑟樂團]]、<ref name="weever">[http://techcrunch.com/2011/06/07/ning-and-ustream-launch-in-depth-integration-to-allow-creators-to-stream-live-video/ Ning And Ustream Launch In-Depth Integration To Allow Creators To Stream Live Video] {{Wayback|url=http://techcrunch.com/2011/06/07/ning-and-ustream-launch-in-depth-integration-to-allow-creators-to-stream-live-video/ |date=20160304041816 }}, Leena Rao, TechCrunch, June 7, 2011</ref>暮光之城系列<ref name="twilightsaga">[http://www.forbes.com/2009/06/30/ning-social-media-cmo-network-ning.html/ Ning Nuzzles Up To Advertisers] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130102214656/http://www.forbes.com/2009/06/30/ning-social-media-cmo-network-ning.html/ |date=2013-01-02 }}, Helen Coster, Forbes, June 30, 2009</ref>、[[東尼·霍克_(運動員)|東尼·霍克]]等<ref name="shredordie">[http://www.dirtforge.com/home/item/80-shred-or-die-skateboard-memories-straight-talk-tony-hawk/ SHRED OR DIE: Straight Up SK8 Memories & Some Straight Talk From Tony Hawk] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dirtforge.com/home/item/80-shred-or-die-skateboard-memories-straight-talk-tony-hawk/ |date=20120327220313 }}, Fidel Gonzales, Dirt Forge, Mar 25, 2010</ref>。

